							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/copyright" rel="tag">copyright</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/doctorow" rel="tag">Doctorow</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/extradition-2" rel="tag">extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/libya" rel="tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mckinnon" rel="tag">McKinnon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/odwyer" rel="tag">O'Dwyer</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/pipa" rel="tag">PIPA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rendition" rel="tag">rendition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sopa" rel="tag">SOPA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
