				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/bishopsgate" rel="tag">Bishopsgate</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cctv" rel="tag">CCTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/hackers" rel="tag">hackers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/id" rel="tag">ID</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ira" rel="tag">IRA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rfid" rel="tag">RFID</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/technology-2" rel="tag">technology</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/terrorism-2" rel="tag">terrorism</a>			</span>
						
